reviewText: I like collecting official anime dvds from Japan cuz they're so expensive!! And only 2 episodes per disc, what??? I never got why Japan sells 2 episodes for a whopping $60 but whatever. Anyways I'm a Haruhi fan and found this here for a really good price and got it for collectors purposes. It comes with two discs, a sticker set and Emiri Kimidori postcards!
